title: Hospitality Analysis Using Power-bi
description: A Hospitality Analytics Dashboard built using Power BI DAX to analyze revenue, occupancy rates, ADR, and booking performance. It includes interactive filters, KPI tracking, and booking platform analysis to help optimize business decisions.

title: Wine Quality Prediction using MLflow
description: This project implements a machine learning pipeline for predicting wine quality using MLflow for experiment tracking. It includes data preprocessing, model training, evaluation, and deployment. The dataset consists of physicochemical properties of wine, and the model predicts its quality based on these features.

title: SN corp Sales Analysis
description: SN Corp Dashboard tracks sales, costs, and profits (749.37K, 383.00K, 366.37K) from 01/01/2017 to 31/12/2020, with visualizations like heatmaps, bar charts, and pie charts for regional and product insights.

title: Diwali Sales Analysis using python
description: Diwali Sales Analysis using Python visualization, including data cleansing and exploratory data analysis (EDA) to uncover trends and insights in sales data.

title: Sales analysis using the DAX
description: Sales analysis performed using DAX queries to analyze and extract key insights from the sales data.
